=== Implementation Notes ===

- Added IsReplay bool to both Tick and Bar DTOs (mdtick/mdtick.go).
- Default value false — real-time ticks/bars are unaffected.
- publisher.go: PublishTick/PublishBar now use PublishMsg with
  X-Ant-Replay: 1 header when IsReplay is true (ADR-0009 §2.1).
- Downstream consumers (factorsvc, quantengine) can filter on this header
  to suppress factor/signal re-emission during replay.

